flow-state|creative_movement_social_exchange_deep_focus_physical_rhythm|paired|creative_movement|social_exchange|deep_focus|physical_rhythm|Why ideas grow through exchange|This pattern works through a close link between Creative Movement and Social Exchange. Ideas open the work, while conversation, feedback, or shared thinking reveals what has energy and what needs changing.|It may show up because the person often trusts possibilities more when they can meet a live response. The exchange makes the idea easier to test before it becomes too fixed.|It protects co-created clarity and responsive originality. The trade-off is that Deep Focus and Physical Rhythm may need deliberate space so the idea can gain substance and reset.|active|flow-state::creative_movement_social_exchange_deep_focus_physical_rhythm::paired
